   - Returns value between 0.80 and 0.95

4. detectCardsNeedingReformulation(): Promise<CardWithFSRS[]>
   - Identifies cards with consistently high response times (>30s avg)
   - Flags cards with high lapse rate (>3 lapses)
   - Suggests split into multiple cards
